data.description: This fantastic and charming Two-story home is in the Cibolo Valley Ranch Subdivision. This four-bedroom, three full-bath, and one-half-bath home boasts high ceilings, an open floor plan, and a gourmet kitchen with abundant cabinet space, perfect for hosting friends and family.The stone and brick masonry and the Juliette balcony create an abundance of curb appeal and an inviting entrance into this impressive home. The Primary bedroom is on the main floor and features a large walk-in closet and en-suite bathroom with double vanity. Upstairs is a game room for entertainment, and the secondary bedrooms are located there. Take advantage of the opportunity to make this house your next home.
